            Anonymous microblogging

ABOUT
=====

Tokumei is written in rc, the Plan 9 shell, using the werc minimal web
framework. The front end uses the Materialize CSS/JS library.

For an introduction to rc, see <http://rc.cat-v.org/>.
For an introduction to werc, see <http://werc.cat-v.org/>.
For an introduction to Materialize, see <http://materializecss.com/>.

Many thanks to uriel and cat-v for werc.

